# Public DevView docs search allowlist.
#
# Historical docs remain on disk as legacy migration inputs. Default ripgrep
# public-doc checks should scan only the canonical public DevView docs below;
# use `devview report-legacy-artifacts --json` for the full legacy inventory.
docs/**
!docs/
!docs/index.md
!docs/install.md
!docs/cli-reference.md
!docs/troubleshooting.md
!docs/concept/
docs/concept/**
!docs/concept/README.md
!docs/concept/devview-terminology.md
